    <b><i><u>What Keeps Me Safe?</u></i></b><br/>
    <br/>
    Our abilities to not read your stored cache cookies is a start. We do not
    care what you are searching for, nor have any requests to shove ads in your
    face like our competitors. We are not concerning ourselves with your online
    presence time. And we are also anonymizing your IP address. Your real IP Address
    will be displayed on your profile "Deck" alongside with your Fake IP Address.<br/>
