    <br/>
    <b><i><u>Why do I see ads?</u></i></b><br/>
    <br/>
    While we do not actively collect your cache and store it for customized ad placement,
    we have taken Google Ads and integrated them into the website for assistance on financial
    stability. The ads are located in very selected spots throughout the website,
    in which are visible, but not actively being pushed directly into your feed directly.
    Thus granting you the ability to see your friends posts and activities without
    scrolling throughout several ads that do not apply to you. Instead we place them
    on different aspects of our site just to show them, but not actively shove them
    in your face like our competitors. <br/>
    <br/>
    <b><i><u>What trackers are you using?</u></i></b><br/>
    <br/>
    We are primarly using Google Tracking only to monitor where are users are coming
    from. We are not storing any active information from you directly. You will
    see your IP Address on your profile page, however, that is active collecting and
    not storing anything. We are using Google Tracking, not to store any information,
    but to gather a monthly report on discovering where are most active users are located
    at in order to provide new resources for the development of Cyber Deck to
    cater to our broad range of users.<br/>
